<p>If your main goals revolve around functional training using bodyweight and <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28129277/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">cable exercises</a>, Titan Fitness has got you covered. Their functional trainer uses a classic cable machine design with built-in storage and some functional training options at the top.&nbsp;</p>



